<item>
            <title>[LU-16607] Speed up some sanity-lnet test cases</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16607</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;some of the router test cases in sanity-lnet (e.g. test_101) take a long time to complete because the IPs used to setup gateways/routes are totally fake. The tests go a lot faster if we use IPs on the same network as the interface used for LNet.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
